channel.title: Vans Warped Tour 2008
channel.description:
I got tickets :)! Anyway, I'm sure the majority know what Warped Tour is, but if you don't:
It's 3 stages, different bands play on each stage, about 80 bands play, and you can walk around to the stage you want to be at (to see which bands you want to) and after bands play most of them just walk around the area or have booths for signing. Anyway, the closest Warped Tour show for me is in Atlanta, GA, and I live in Columbus, MS.
Anyway, here's the list of bands, which I've rated lol 1-5 stars, cause I have to decide which bands I want to see:
***** A Day To Remember ***** The Audition ***** Angels and Airwaves ***** As I Lay Dying ***** The Devil Wears Prada ***** Forever the Sickest Kids ***** Four Year Strong ***** From First to Last ***** Greeley Estates ***** Madina Lake ***** Motionless In White ***** Say Anything ***** Story of the Year
**** The Academy Is... **** Alesana **** Evergreen Terrace **** Every Avenue **** Farewell **** Gym Class Heroes **** Just Surrender **** Mayday Parade **** Norma Jean **** Relient K **** The Secret Handshake **** Valencia **** We The Kings
*** 3OH!3 *** Alamance *** Cobra Starship *** Dead Legend *** Every Time I Die *** Family Force 5 *** Jack's Mannequin *** Pierce the Veil *** Set Your Goals
** Against Me! ** Anberlin ** CrashCarBurn ** The Color Fred ** The Dillinger Escape Plan ** Disco Ensemble ** The Higher ** Katy Perry ** Matisyahu ** Maylene and the Sons of Disaster ** Protest the Hero
* Add. Verse * The Aggrolites * Be Your Own Pet * Beat Union * Bedouin Soundclash * Blake * The Briggs * Broadway Calls * The Bronx * Charlotte Sometimes * Culture Shock Camp * Dante * The Fabulous Rudies * Gaslight Anthem * Gil Mantera's Party Dream * Hangar 18 * Horrorpops * The Lordz * Massive Monkees * MC Chris * ORESKABAND * Othello * The Pink Spiders * The Pinker Tones * Piotta * The Recovering * Reel Big Fish * The Saint Alvia Cartel * Shwayze * Skeet Skeet * Steve Steadham / Citizen X * Street Drum Corps Presents BANG! * Street Dogs * Tat
I've never been to a concert before, so this is big for me :)
